I made the salad according to the recipe with two exceptions: I added sliced fresh water chestnuts and grilled the chicken. I took a huge bowl of the salad to a potluck dinner and it was a great success! It was eaten so quickly I barely got any. There was nothing left in the bowl but two leaves of watercress and a tiny slice of waterchestnut. Totally delicious!